    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Sentiment News and Tic-tac-toe]]></title>
        <id>https://amentfirm.github.io/blog/sentiment-news-and-tic-tac-toe</id>
        <link href="https://amentfirm.github.io/blog/sentiment-news-and-tic-tac-toe"/>
        <updated>2023-02-24T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[We used SnowNLP and pysenti to compute two sentiment scores for each HK news that we scrapped daily. Using these scores, we visualize the news in a sentiment square. From this visualization, we can roughly know how happy/sad daily HK news is. On the other hand, we started our game development journal. Inspired by the simple tic-tac-toe implementation by Fellipe Utakausing tailwind and react, we implemented similarly our own tic-tac-toe game.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>We used <a href="https://pypi.org/project/snownlp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SnowNLP</a> and <a href="https://pypi.org/project/pysenti/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">pysenti</a> to compute two sentiment scores for each HK news that we scrapped daily. Using these scores, we visualize the news in a <a href="/docs/NewsViz/SentimentNews">sentiment square</a>. From this visualization, we can roughly know how happy/sad daily HK news is. On the other hand, we started our game development journal. Inspired by the simple tic-tac-toe implementation by <a href="https://reactjsexample.com/a-tic-tac-toe-game-made-with-react-and-tailwind-css/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fellipe Utaka</a>using tailwind and react, we implemented similarly our own <a href="/docs/Games/TicTacToe">tic-tac-toe game</a>.</p><p>我哋用咗<a href="https://pypi.org/project/snownlp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SnowNLP</a>同<a href="https://pypi.org/project/pysenti/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">pysenti</a>去計每單香港每日新聞嘅情感分數，然後用呢兩個情感分數將新聞顯示係一個<a href="/docs/NewsViz/SentimentNews">二維情感平面</a>上。通過呢個顯示方法，我哋可以大概見到香港每日新聞係開心多定係傷心多。此外，我哋亦踏上寫遊戲嘅旅程。睇到<a href="https://reactjsexample.com/a-tic-tac-toe-game-made-with-react-and-tailwind-css/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fellipe Utaka</a>簡單地用tailwind同react去寫井字過三關，我哋都寫左一個相似嘅<a href="/docs/Games/TicTacToe">井字過三關</a>。</p>]]></content>
