    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[HK News on a Sphere]]></title>
        <id>https://amentfirm.github.io/blog/news-on-sphere</id>
        <link href="https://amentfirm.github.io/blog/news-on-sphere"/>
        <updated>2023-02-10T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[We added a cronjob on our server to scrape HK news daily and store them on FireStore. Then we implemented a query to search for the news and used the technique demonstrated by raizensoft (video here) to display HK news on a sphere. To display arbitrary numbers of news evenly on the sphere, we used spherical Fibonacci mapping.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>We added a cronjob on our server to scrape HK news daily and store them on FireStore. Then we implemented a query to <a href="/docs/NewsViz/SearchNews">search for the news</a> and used the technique demonstrated by <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@raizensoft" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">raizensoft</a> (video <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqpUsk3HWic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>) to display HK <a href="/docs/NewsViz/SphereNews">news on a sphere</a>. To display arbitrary numbers of news evenly on the sphere, we used <a href="https://doi.org/10.1145/2816795.2818131" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">spherical Fibonacci mapping</a>.</p><p>我哋加咗個cornjob係server上每日爬香港新聞同儲存係FireStore上面。然後我哋寫咗個query去<a href="/docs/NewsViz/SearchNews">搵香港新閒</a>同用咗<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@raizensoft" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">raizensoft</a>係<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xqpUsk3HWic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">呢喥</a>示範嘅技巧將每日嘅<a href="/docs/NewsViz/SphereNews">香港新閒顯示係球上面</a>。我哋用咗<a href="https://doi.org/10.1145/2816795.2818131" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">spherical Fibonacci mapping</a>將任意數目嘅新閒平均地放係球上面。</p>]]></content>
